The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Lawrence Carpenter, Appellant.

Judgment, Supreme Court, New York County, rendered on March 17, 1978, unanimously affirmed. The order of this court entered on April 22, 1980 [75 AD2d —] is hereby vacated. No opinion. Concur—Birns, J. P., Fein, Sandler, Markewich and Bloom, JJ.
